deploy(string,string).notice: This is the entry point for the Sphinx deploy command. It makes a few FFI calls to         TypeScript logic that's shared with the Hardhat plugin. Note that this command must         perform all read and write operations to the blockchain from within Solidity instead         of using a provider object in TypeScript. Otherwise, an error will be thrown because         we can't create a provider object for the in-process Anvil node from outside of         Solidity.
